Confidential company
Please see Job Details for Apply instructions
Saved!
Job Details
UAE based Diamond Trading Company is looking for Senior Diamond Sales Manager, interested candidates with following experience can send their CV with photo to  uaerecruitment2014@gmail.com
Should have sound knowledge in  loose diamonds quality and the demand and availability.
Should have very good network with middle east and India and HK based customers.
Good negotiation skill.
Understanding the market trend – demand and pricing and availability.
Meeting the sales target.
Should have through knowledge on yearly sales budget.
Handling exhibitions around the global.
Team building to meet the organization requirement.
Diamonds Assortment co-ordination.
Guiding the assortment team on quality and the customer requirement.
Stock management as per the sales requirement.
Exhibition  planning and execution.
